<P>LAMENTABLE Newes, Shewing the wonderfull de|liuerance of Mai&s;ter Edmond Pet Sayler, and Mai&s;ter of a Ship, dwelling in Seething Lane in London, neere Barking Church. With other &s;trange things late|ly hapned concerning the&s;e great windes and tempe&s;tuous wea|ther, both at Sea and Lande.</P>
