<FIGDESC>two men in a ship, drawing something from the water</FIGDESC>
</FIGURE></P>
<P>Imprinted at London by <HI>T.C.</HI> for William Barley, dwelling ouer again&s;t Cree-church, neere Algate. 1613.</P>
